Rating: 4
An easy to make and delicious way to serve chicken. The only thing I did differently was to flatten the chicken breasts prior to browning. They cook faster this way and because they are thin, the meat is more flavored by the sauce than a thick breast would be. Be sure to serve this with Chinese sticky rice (short grain) as the sauce clings to this kind of rice and it is really delicious.

